description: Replacement brush head for clarisonic skin cleansing system fits all clarisonic models. Brush head should be replaced every 3 months. Safe for use on acne prone skin. Velvet like bristle tips are uniquely textured to provide an extra gentle cleansing action on gentle skin.

title: Clarisonic Aria Sonic Skin Cleansing Kit, White
description: Clarisonic new ARIA sonic cleansing system is a professional caliber cleansing brush that uses gentle sonic micro message action to helps keep your skin looking young, vibrant and healthy. title: Jojoba Oil, Golden Organic 100% Pure 4 oz
description: Jojoba oil comes from the beans of the shrub like plant, simmondsia chinensis. This is the highest grade certified organic, cold pressed oil (actually a liquid plant wax). It is bright and golden in color and is regarded as the most favored in the carrier oil family because of its advanced molecular stability. Also makes a great scalp cleanser for the hair, and is equally wonderful for the skin because it has absorption properties that are similar to our skins own sebum.

title: Botanical Beauty ORGANIC ROSEHIP OIL 100% Pure. For Face, Hair and Body. 0.5 Fl.oz.- 15 ml.
description: Botanical Beauty Organic RoseHip Oil is reach in essential fatty acids, vitamins and minerals. It has natural antioxidant properties and is slightly astringent.
